CARE -- CALIFORNIA; PROPOSITION 99 (TOBACCO TAX); PROPOSITION 98 (SCHOOL 
DISTRICT FUNDS); CALIFORNIA -- SCHOOLS -- FINANCES; DEUKMEJIAN, GEORGE 
</P>
