INVESTMENTS -- NORTHERN IRELAND; NORTHERN IRELAND -- LABOR; AFFIRMATIVE ACTION; 
EMPLOYMENT DISCRIMINATION; RELIGIOUS DISCRIMINATION 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
