<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The actors playing the Capulet parents in "Romeo and Juliet" at the Grove 
Shakespeare Festival in Garden Grove are Daniel Bryan Cartmell and Pam 
Franklin. Incorrect names were given in Monday's Calendar. 
</P>
</TEXT>
