in Newport Beach. ; Photo, An army may march on its stomach, but these Marines 
wasted no time taking off their boots. ; Photo, Linda Easter and her mother, 
Dorothy Herman, at Linda's Day Care in Corona del Mar were first worried then 
amused as the Marine reservists marched past on suburban Marguerite Avenue. ; 
