RAUB, RICHARD 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA062789-0130 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 75452 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
June 27, 1989, Tuesday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Part 6; Page 9; Column 1; Entertainment Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
1009 words 
</P>
